categories: Category:Sith Lords of the reconstituted Sith Empire

nodes.text: Prejad was a Sith Lord of the Sith Empire who fought on Ilum during the Galactic War. Prejad and two other Sith Lords, Wenom and Shados, killed the Galactic Republic's alien commandos and took over their forward camp, leading the Republic to counterstrike and kill the three. Prejad wielded a red double-bladed lightsaber.
